# `./gradlew :tools:jmdict-builder:run` from jmdict-simplified.
app/src/main/assets/jmdict.db

# --- Builder caches (downloaded zips / extracted JSON) ---
tools/jmdict-builder/.cache/
# IDE-driven JVM compile output for the builder tool.
tools/jmdict-builder/bin/

